The 4 Points of serverless:
1. No infra to provision and configure
2. On-demand execution
3. Auto-scaling
4. Per-second billing


Knative architecture:
1. Kuberentes
2. Istio
3. Knative
  a. Serving
  b. Eventing


GKE has a Beta feature to install Istio with a checkbox

The 4 functions of Knative Serving:
1. Service (the microservice container)
2. Routing (manage istio functions)
3. Configuration (like env vars and stuff)
4. Revision (point in time snap of code and config together)

Knative Routing:
Source (reads events)
Broker (receives events from source)
Trigger (bridges broker and service)
Service (App consumes from Broker)
